{"tid":2390530,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【奴性訓練】林鄭繼續連封四城，香港人繼續專重「科學」力量齊心全力抗疫","createTime":"2021-02-01T15:04:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T12:00:10.000Z","uid":88743,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ba9835bc41f79b8b2c2fd2bd58297067e36d3911","tid":2390530,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T15:04:51.000Z","msg":"何栢良：倡大廈有一宗確診個案即封　<br />\n政府昨晚7時將藍田麗港城第5及第7座列為「受限區域」，封樓進行強制新冠肺炎病毒檢測。行動於今早7時30分完成，約460人接受採樣，當中沒有確診個案，行動中另有60戶無人應門。香港大學感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良批評，麗港城爆疫發生十多日才做封區檢測不及時，建議要走在病毒前，倡每當有大廈出現一宗確診個案，而專家評估該座大廈有高危因素，便應即時封鎖大廈及檢測，非採用現時的「突襲式」封區。   <br />\n<br />\n梁卓偉：要相信科學，不可以有政治考慮，如果唔係實出事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aSX5kTE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaSX5kTE.gif&h=9d70e8a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n林鄭連封四區：<br />\n<br />\n政府就元朗指明「受限區域」作出限制與檢測宣告及強制檢測公告<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202102/01/P2021020100674.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202102%2F01%2FP2021020100674.htm&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl5bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=4e88801f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202102/01/P2021020100674.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n政府就尖沙咀指明「受限區域」作出限制與檢測宣告及強制檢測公告<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202102/01/P2021020100660.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202102%2F01%2FP2021020100660.htm&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl5bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=6f3eeeec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202102/01/P2021020100660.htm</a>    <br />\n       <br />\n政府就九龍城指明「受限區域」作出限制與檢測宣告及強制檢測公告<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202102/01/P2021020100731.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202102%2F01%2FP2021020100731.htm&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl5bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=34d6e2d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202102/01/P2021020100731.htm</a>   <br />\n   <br />\n政府就油麻地指明「受限區域」作出限制與檢測宣告及強制檢測公告<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202102/01/P2021020100739.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202102%2F01%2FP2021020100739.htm&d=FyOxfEvlGqeE3CGJWKQQl5bpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=74f16c59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202102/01/P2021020100739.htm</a>   <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人反應：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5CyHquO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5CyHquO.gif&h=9534199e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n香港人：<br />\n哈哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁撚鐘意返工丫嗱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾警察捉抵撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e6d288674621196143de6fbe960029bdc8e92d","tid":2390530,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-01T15:06:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OAPGF40.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOAPGF40.gif&h=ede6dd9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"878d0e1d89a5b071fa605fc29cd737d379ba0463","tid":2390530,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":